{"tid":16496,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（生果報）人事顧問：減20%是必須！","createTime":"2016-12-01T12:54:31.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T13:16:54.000Z","uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5d194b4500b202e66caa37ff732713d22871bfa0","tid":16496,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T12:54:31.000Z","msg":"「張小姐，本人到一間大公司見一了個Senior Executive的職位，&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;之後公司只offer 我要求待遇的八成，但要我答應銀碼之後才給我看其他合約內容。這是否很奇怪？<br />\n<br />\nCut 20%，一般人會去嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到我答應後，人事部經理又口頭說要6個月試用期，首三個月沒有prorata bonus、沒有醫療，又是要我答應後才能看合約內容，是有誠意請我嗎？其實他們這做這些小動作有甚麼目的意義？&hellip;&hellip;」"},{"pid":"7a3f6118bdc1eaa8b129ec9c8953329c3015dde6","tid":16496,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T12:56:51.000Z","msg":"答：<br />\n<br />\n公司尤其人事部認為只要牌頭大、字號老，能夠入來做足以光耀門楣，將來寫落CV都夠照，用錢都買唔到，既然畀你機會有status有exposure，<span style=\"color: red;\">貼錢來做都是應該。</span><br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n在你看來的小動作，在人事部經理的角度，是捍衞公司的必須！人家是大公司，高高在上即是upper，你是求職者，千萬不能忘記你有「求」於人在先，<span style=\"color: red;\">做lower的乖乖聽話就是了，做乜咁多聲氣？</span><br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n你如此沉不住氣，這份工作究竟是否適合你？即使肯忍讓你又可以忍得幾幾耐讓幾多？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSOURCR:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=55991053&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161201\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D55991053%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161201&d=NX17wA0xajt0Xz52GN5L9gv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=11009650\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D55991053%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161201&h=9c1dca9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=55991053&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161201</a>"},{"pid":"cf77b21fa2a156bbbe7c9770e